---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="mt-auto border-t border-slate-200 bg-white py-12 dark:border-slate-800 dark:bg-slate-950">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 text-center sm:px-6 lg:px-8">

        <div class="mb-8 flex justify-center">
            <a
                    href="https://teachable.com/experts"
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noopener noreferrer"
                    class="group flex flex-col items-center gap-3 transition-transform hover:scale-105"
            >
                <img
                        src="/images/ui/teachableexpert-badge.png"
                        alt="Official Teachable Expert Badge"
                        class="h-16 w-auto object-contain drop-shadow-sm grayscale transition-all group-hover:grayscale-0 dark:brightness-110"
                />
                <span class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-expert-500">Official Vetted Partner</span>
            </a>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-4 text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">
            Teachable Expert
        </div>

        <p class="mb-6 text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">
            Custom API architecture, webhook development, and advanced data integrations <br class="hidden sm:block" />
            for high-volume Teachable creators.
        </p>

        <div class="text-xs text-slate-400 dark:text-slate-500">
            &copy; {currentYear} Teachable Expert. All rights reserved. <br/>
            <span class="mt-2 inline-block">
                Teachable Expert is an independent consultancy and official Teachable Partner. <br class="hidden sm:block" />
                Teachable is a registered trademark of Teachable, Inc.
            </span>
        </div>

    </div>
</footer>